                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The additional rounds do not consume additional ammunition."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "At rank 4 or higher, this mod guarantees that at least 2 rounds will be fired for every 1 round of ammunition expended."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "At maximum rank, this mod grants an 100% chance to fire one additional round (2 rounds/shot) and a 20% chance to fire two additional rounds (3 rounds/shot)."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Equipping this mod and Lethal Torrent simultaneously will provide 180% multishot, giving the sidearm a 100% chance to fire one additional round (2 rounds/shot) and an 80% chance to fire two additional rounds (3 rounds/shot)."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For weapons that fire multiple pellets (i.e. a Bronco ) the pellet count is multiplied by the multishot value."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "A Bronco with a rank 5 Barrel Diffusion will fire 7 × ( 1 + 1.2 ) = 15.4 pellets, meaning it has a 100% chance to fire 15 pellets and a 40% chance to fire 1 extra pellet."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The in-game UI will consider any possible multishot capabilities when showing total damage numbers, and does not represent single-projectile damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Total damage displayed does not represent the actual damage per shot, but the expected average damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Barrel Diffusion",
                  "pageId": 22770,
                  "revisionId": 2685823,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Equipping this mod increases the status chance of a weapon indirectly. This is due to the possibility of shooting more than one projectile."
                }
